OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FA new #26.5m hospice has officially
OL,7,Fopened that "will serve the people of
OL,8,FGreater Manchester for generations to
OL,9,Fcome".
OL,11,FThe Moya Cole Hospice in Heald Green
OL,12,Fhas 21 ensuite bedrooms, private
OL,13,Foutdoor terraces and dedicated space
OL,14,Ffor counselling, patient and family
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,FThe project has been ten years in the
OL,18,Fmaking and thousands of people have
OL,19,Fhelped fundraise for the new build.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
