OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FThe hospice, formerly known as St
OL,7,FAnn's, has served the community for
OL,8,Fthe past 55 years but their old
OL,9,Fbuilding was no longer fit for
OL,10,Fpurpose. With the help of donors and
OL,11,Fsupporters, they have now created a
OL,12,Fnew purpose-built hospice on land next
OL,13,Fdoor.
OL,15,FStaff believe the new hospice will
OL,16,Ftransform the experience of patients
OL,17,Fand those close to them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FThe hospice also said their "Being You
OL,7,FCentre" will greatly benefit patients
OL,8,Fwith more space for counselling,
OL,9,Fpatient and family support, and
OL,10,Fcomplementary therapies as well as
OL,11,Fdedicated space for palliative
OL,12,Frehabilitation.
OL,14,FRachel McMillan, the hospice's Chief
OL,15,FExecutive said: "We had one chance to
OL,16,Fget this right. We had to make sure
OL,17,Fwe're future-proof - that the design,
OL,18,Fand the environment isn't just right
OL,19,Fnow but right for decades to come
OL,20,Fbecause this is our legacy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,F"You only have to speak to the
OL,7,Fpatients and staff and volunteers and
OL,8,Ffamilies to know this is right and
OL,9,Fthis is what the future of hospice
OL,10,Fcare should look like."
OL,12,FFormer police officer Mike Morris was
OL,13,Fthe first patient to be given a tour
OL,14,Fof the new facility.
OL,16,FMike, 67, has stage 4 prostate cancer
OL,17,Fand is an outpatient at the hospice.
OL,18,FHe said the support he's received has
OL,19,Fmade a massive difference in dealing
OL,20,Fwith his diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FMike said: "It's made me feel alive
OL,7,Fagain in a way. It's certainly gave me
OL,8,Fa lot of hope. You suddenly realise
OL,9,F'well hang on, I can still do a bit
OL,10,Fhere...all's not done yet... so let's
OL,11,Fplan everything out'.
OL,13,F"I've got to say, the last three and a
OL,14,Fhalf years have been the best years of
OL,15,Fmy life because I've not taken life
OL,16,Ffor granted. I've not taken my family
OL,17,Ffor granted. It makes you treasure it
OL,18,Fmore. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FMike said he was particularly
OL,7,Fimpressed by the lay out and design of
OL,8,Fthe new site. He said: "I think it's
OL,9,Ffantastic. It's so nice and bright and
OL,10,FI love being out in this garden. It's
OL,11,Fgood for me with my wheelchair because
OL,12,Feverything is flat and accessible. and
OL,13,Fthere are nice wide doorways so I can
OL,14,Fget everywhere."
OL,16,FAmanda Walton's mother, Jackie
OL,17,FClayton, died at the hospice in 2018
OL,18,Fon the morning of her 64th birthday.
OL,19,FShe had been diagnosed with kidney
OL,20,Fcancer two years earlier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FAmanda said before coming to the
OL,7,Fhospice her mother's pain was "off the
OL,8,Fscale" and she had "stopped smiling".
OL,10,FHowever within a few days of being at
OL,11,Fthe hospice and receiving pain
OL,12,Fmanagement, Jackie started to "come
OL,13,Fback to her family".
OL,15,FDuring the eight weeks she spent at
OL,16,Fthe hospice Jackie and her family were
OL,17,Fable to celebrate several birthdays
OL,18,Fand Mothers' Day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778677870
OL,3,CNew hospice opens providing end-of-
OL,4,Clife care for 'generations of people'
OL,6,FAmanda said: "We could come in every
OL,7,Fsingle day. There were no time limits
OL,8,Fon how long we could spend with her
OL,9,Fand that's important when someone's
OL,10,Fscared and lonely. It (the hospice)
OL,11,Fmade a massive difference. It's the
OL,12,Fcare that people don't know they need
OL,13,Fat a time when it's needed the most.
OL,15,FOver the past eight years the family
OL,16,Fhas fundraised nearly #70,000 in
OL,17,FJackie's memory, which went towards
OL,18,Fbuilding the new hospice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
